Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were waiting at the office of Ran's mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:09.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We met the former All-Japan women's\Njudo champion in the 70kg class...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:10.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Her name was Arisawa Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Arisawa Yuuko (37)\NJudo Martial Artist
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When her husband, Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, requested a\Nconsultation over a recent stalker problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A meeting was set to meet with them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} revealed he had suddenly been called to a wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was planned that he would meet them at 9:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we arrived at the set time, we discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strangled body of Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lawyer Kisaki began to find Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}'s behavior suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But her alibi was solid in that she had\Nshared a meal with us at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was only the ten minute period\Nwhere she went to the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a short time frame, is it possible for her to have\Nkilled Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who had been at a wake previously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A desperate crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A splendid resurgence{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ges the solution to the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou and Eri's combined deduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makes a tag-team move on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they have call forwarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, if Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called here from\Nyour office, it would forward to his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, since no one answered, the service would have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, before you two made it to the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in order to confirm the appointment for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the call wasn't forwarded...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It went to the answering machine after ten rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe the husband hadn't come home yet, so his cell was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just that phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Near the closet where the body was\Ndiscovered is the door to the garage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trash there was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it easier to take it out if it's left there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the position, but the contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:04:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A large amount of match books from the western-\Nstyle restaurant we ate at earlier had accumulated there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she doesn't smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her husband, a heavy smoker, was likely\Nresponsible for bringing them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's a regular customer at that same restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did she say he had zero tolerance for their\Nfood, which caused her to always go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we have Dad investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he can find a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather sell my soul to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The devil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found a listening device?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This makes it more likely that the victim was the target of a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, we found two items in the victim's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first was found in the inside the pocket of his suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the victim's missing ring wasn't taken after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which makes the question why he removed it to his pocket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In his coat pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this black necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be the murder weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even look like it's been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means it's brand new?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I give Dad a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad did say he was going drinking with\Nthe master of Poirot and the others, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt he'll be drunk just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just quiet down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom has something she wants to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eri does?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I doubt he'll be able to look into much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not really anything important, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not anything important, then don't call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, don't hang up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you see the former All-Japan champion as suspicious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the crime occurred, she was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since you don't even know where the victim went to a wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes it impossible to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the answer is simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her alibi is solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best evidence is that you talked to the victim yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could have been some sort of deceit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ron?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm at the table practicing with some of the neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's all, you'll need to find someone else to be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did Dad say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was busy playing mahjong, so we'll have to find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, even then, he wasn't really playing mahjong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a tape, a tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know he used it a number of times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get nearly the same sound by using one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't know their whereabouts at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit can decide where to cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The husband didn't want it to be known...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the reason for the underhanded trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that his trick was seen through...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without him realizing just how it would come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite the few unexplained points that remain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can assume, from Arisawa Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nrecent claims about being troubled by a stalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That someone came to this house, confronted\NShirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as he was returning from the wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ended it by taking his necktie and strangling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it possible that the reason Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nremoved his wedding ring and necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because he was readying to bathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stalker must've been hiding in the bathroom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he was discovered by Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, he took the necktie, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only remaining question is just why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a sealed necktie in his coat pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps someone asked him to buy it for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wakes are generally quite urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible someone may have been required to go\Ndirectly from work, and had to ask him to buy it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, in the end, they were unable to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it wouldn't be unusual\Nat all for him to have an extra necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When 9:00 came around earlier, we were just leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drive from the hotel restaurant to here takes at least ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wife Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was just\Nleaving the restaurant with us at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, we have no connection to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May we leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to find out whether or not anyone\Nsuspicious was seen leaving the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go look into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I speak to you in the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Article 42, sub-paragraph 01 of the penal code.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Criminal offenders that voluntarily surrender before being properly\Nsuspected by authorities may reduce the severity of their sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is why the one I am advising to surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the very Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that strangled her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this some sort of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say so earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the approximate time of the murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had only just finished eating and were\Nleaving the hotel restaurant together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, before that, did you not make a trip to the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was for ten minutes, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In so little time, how could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you only pretended to visit the restroom\Nand instead went to strangle your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Returning after just ten minutes is more than possible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the former All-Japan judo champion for the 70kg class...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And for someone who is currently a dojo's coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I had no clue where my husband went for the wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I get there from the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no call for visting the wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Considering your husband was already at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Already" there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard it too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was his voice on the phone saying he was at a wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I came to their wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're denying hearing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ting was from a tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was to hide his affair, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband was guilty of using that trick\Nconstantly when he was with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would play a recording of patrol\Ncar sirens next to the phone and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A sudden case has come up, so I'll be\Nhome late — go to bed without me."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In actuality, he was drinking at the bar until dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably not the best time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prior to taking a bath, do you normally remove\Nyour wedding band and store it in your pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, if he were going out to meet someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would make a lot of sense, would it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as for that unopened black necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He planned to put it on before returning home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make it appear he had been to a wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he could do that, you strangled\Nhim with a different necktie, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, further evidence is the restaurant matchbooks\Nthat have collected in the garbage by the garage door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your heavy smoker of a husband brought them back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also mentioned that you go to the restaurant on a weekly basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This would mean you both visit that restaurant often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why did you say you only ever go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband has zero tolerance for new food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you always went alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your husband did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw it in that restaurant, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your husband was there happily enjoying a meal with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That restaurant is where they usually frequent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you had only discovered it that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You proceeded to scatter listening devices around the house,\Nand fabricated the story of the stalker to meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as we waited, you invited us to that hotel restaurant for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you contacted your husband on the phone from my office...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You expected him to play something in the\Nbackground that he'd prepared as an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also predicted he would say he'd be\Nhome late and not to wait up for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, you timed when he would be leaving the\Nhotel, and pretended to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then caught your husband in the parking lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where you proceeded to drag him to your car, and strangled him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, you placed him in the trunk of your car
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And came back as if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward, you drove your car with us\Nand the body inside to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:14:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You instructed us to wait here in the living room while you\Ntransported his body from the trunk to the nearby closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And lastly, you called him so we would discover the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was anything I said in the wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That story sure sounds like a plausible one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can probably find out by checking the hotel parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keeping in mind that your husband was punctual...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have been alone in the lot at the time of his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, it should still be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car that your husband drove to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, should he have been in the car of another woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't dare risk having her see your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you couldn't have killed him in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The garage here only has space for one car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, your husband rented a car behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why not investigate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hotel parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, should you riot find a car like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even you, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, can't get out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arisawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is really good at judo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you teach me the inner thigh throw?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you use your opponent's attacking\Npower to your advantage and throw them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You use their power to throw them\Nto the ground and gain points, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using your opponent's power to your advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gaining points...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, back then, didn't Arisawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} teach us how to adjust our seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, do you know how to move the seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a lever on the right side of the seat, and if you pull it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seat will move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car that you ended up driving us back in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the car your husband drove to the hotel, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you demonstrated how to adjust the seats, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your husband is smaller and shorter than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's natural for his seat to be in a different position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should you adjust it on a whim, it would seem suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would also explain your adjusting of the rear-view mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should come as no surprise why you\Ncouldn't find the car in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, you trailed him closely and\Navoided letting him take notice of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he got inside the car, you proceeded to strangle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward, you likely rushed back at full speed to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, due to this, you did not have enough\Ntime to remember the car's position, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really was a strange story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your reason for inviting us to that hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because of the cheap parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when you were expected to pay for the parking ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:17:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite not having gone anywhere else,\Nthe ticket was suspiciously missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is peculiar, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you said you had "lost the ticket," what you really meant\Nwas that you weren't sure where your husband put it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your husband were the type to put things away at random...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be behind the sunvisor, or even in the ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a proper search of the car, I imagine we'll find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hotel parking ticket with your husband's fingerprints on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be the proof that your\Nhusband was also at the hotel tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we check the trunk, we should find\Nevidence that he was moved from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe his hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And possibly even the necktie used as a weapon, as well as his shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as for the shoes that we saw at the entryway tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were likely prepared by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the police come across this evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In his left sock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where my husband usually puts his parking tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if they check there, they should find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could someone like you resort to murder over a mere affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were only an affair, a divorce would have sufficed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other woman was Kajimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} san{\r}'s wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kajimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the gold medalist you mentioned before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wouldn't that give you even more reason to work it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like you weren't acquainted with his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband and I visited Kajimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house often in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a good wife, such a cute child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were the ideal family you see in pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, my husband—he ruined that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I considered the suffering to come, I couldn't live on that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even a divorce would've been enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only by killing him would it be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really never should grow close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we had never visited Kajimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband and his wife wouldn't have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only I had kept my admiration to myself,\Nnone of this would have come to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is merely an assumption, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could your husband have just wanted more attention from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tape trick for an alibi would have only worked\Ntwo, maybe three times before he was found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, when it comes to those matches from the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may as well have told you directly that he went there often.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying my husband wanted me to discover his affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was jealous that you still thought of\NKajimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, despite being married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:20:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He crossed the line and angered you,\Ncaught on fire, and fell to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun that burned Icarus' wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was actually you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all thanks to Dad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the alibi tapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A coincidence, just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Definitely an accidental hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it really a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a deliberate hint, just for Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably too embarassed to say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to find out, here's the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should at least inform him that the case is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I'm still playing mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly, still using those tapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Uncle's back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perverted old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:58.73,title01,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Tonight drinking party has been canceled!\NSorry about that, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - title01}-kun{\r}~!\h\h-Poirot Master
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he'd used this strategy so often\Nbefore, he saw through it instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was able to find his own alibi tapes so\Nquickly because he skipped on the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he tried to play it one more time over the last call, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, we'll have a friend of the groom, Mouri\NKogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, give a congratulatory speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What bad luck, recording that part and accidentally playing it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, quite a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eri...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too, Uncle.
